    GeneratorLpGoalImpl

    public abstract class GeneratorGoalImpl
extends GeneratorElementImpl
implements GeneratorGoal
    An implementation of the model object 'Generator Goal'.

    A goal is passed to a solver as goal (indeed) to be achieved: the goal for solving.

    A goal may have a subGoal, which will have to be solved after this goal has been solved.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Generator
    • Name
    • Selected Solution Display
    • Label
    • Solution
